{"tid":2495221,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"參選人提名期不需披露國籍，當局稱資審會可取相關資料","createTime":"2021-04-19T05:12:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T05:22:52.000Z","uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0516550d40117710eb3c0d247c149bae18bb654d","tid":2495221,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:12:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586502-20210419.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586502-20210419.htm&d=CDYmK9DOGPUFxvwNhHfqxwoLTLCpuPbPc66RZsxrzrI%3D&h=d76fcec9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1586502-20210419.htm&h=cdd0cc12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1586502-20210419.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會有關修改選舉制度的綜合修訂條例草案委員會早上開會，繼續逐條審議條例。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會立法會議員麥美娟關注，目前選委會參選人要在聲明中表明擁護《基本法》和效忠特區，但並無處理有關人士的國籍問題，無問及他是否持有BNO及其他國家護照等，認為有關人士既然參選擔任公職人士，有無持有外國護照都不敢說，並無資格參選。<br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局常任秘書長鄧忍光表示，聲明並無相關要求，但將來資審委會將以表格形式向參選人索取有關資料，再考慮其參選資格，不會要求參選人在提名階段提供相關資料，是因為資料可以被公開閱覽，當局要取得平衡。"},{"pid":"6dfac32ccb03f66119b94924b83dd789810862b6","tid":2495221,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:15:07.000Z","msg":"有外國籍都可以做選委會真係笑撚死，又話愛國，都唔撚知係愛邊個國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"714ec42c28f52678d03f71d5de7f2b19ad5a2383","tid":2495221,"uid":389395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:17:36.000Z","msg":"愛國用把口，點會用個心"},{"pid":"7bbb01bf69931c6a91cd555072528250dba2ab3a","tid":2495221,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:17:46.000Z","msg":"麥美娟好驚同外國人爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaefae8721c2fa636ce87ac3aa840c8d886ef0ca","tid":2495221,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:19:11.000Z","msg":"愛(外)國者治港<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"515a7dc06d709ad49a56694b30a4c8f9768ac26b","tid":2495221,"uid":9542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6dfac32ccb03f66119b94924b83dd789810862b6","tid":2495221,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:15:07.000Z","msg":"有外國籍都可以做選委會真係笑撚死，又話愛國，都唔撚知係愛邊個國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T05:22:52.000Z","msg":"十成班大陸人自己都外國藉啦，一定要保佢地"}]}